      <pubDate>Sat, 06 Jun 2026 07:06:22 +0000</pubDate>
      <category>The core argument is that plain text formats, specifically Markdown, are the optimal
        foundation for building AI-powered workflows and knowledge systems due to their efficiency,
        compatibility with agents, and version control capabilities. The traditional reliance on
        binary formats like Word and PowerPoint creates inefficiencies and limitations for agents.
